{"text_id":10164,"tokens":["Our"," work"," investigates"," the"," viability"," of"," using"," large","-","scale"," cosmic"," microwave"," background"," (","CM","B",")"," polarization"," to"," constrain"," the"," epoch"," of"," re","ionization","."," We"," employ"," a"," model","-","independent"," approach",","," avoiding"," reliance"," on"," specific"," re","ionization"," models"," by"," focusing"," on"," observable"," polarization"," statistics","."," We"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," phase"," evolution"," of"," CMB"," polarization"," patterns"," carries"," information"," about"," the"," ionization"," and"," recombination"," history"," of"," the"," universe","."," Using"," a"," Markov"," chain"," Monte"," Carlo"," sampler",","," we"," explore"," the"," posterior"," distribution"," of"," re","ionization"," parameters"," directly"," from"," the"," observed"," polarization"," data","."," Our"," results"," suggest"," that"," future"," CMB"," polarization"," experiments"," can"," achieve"," competitive"," constraints"," on"," the"," optical"," depth"," of"," re","ionization",","," the"," duration"," of"," the"," re","ionization"," process",","," and"," the"," amplitude"," of"," primordial"," B","-","modes","."," By"," bypassing"," model","-","dependent"," assumptions",","," our"," work"," p","aves"," the"," way"," for"," robust"," and"," reliable"," constraints"," on"," re","ionization"," solely"," based"," on"," observational"," data","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}